parts.text:
**Asian**

* **Soups:**
    * Hot and Sour Soup (Chinese)
    * Miso Soup (Japanese)
    * Tom Yum Soup (Thai)
    * Pho (Vietnamese)
    * Laksa (Malaysian)
* **Stews:**
    * Beef Rendang (Indonesian)
    * Japanese Curry
    * Chicken Teriyaki (Japanese)
    * Pad See Ew (Thai)
    * Stir-fried Beef with Snow Peas and Carrots (Chinese)
* **Hot Drinks:**
    * Green Tea (various origins)
    * Matcha (Japanese green tea)
    * Ginger Tea (Chinese)
    * Turmeric Tea (Indian)
    * Chrysanthemum Tea (Chinese)

**Mediterranean**

* **Soups:**
    * Minestrone (Italian)
    * Gazpacho (Spanish)
    * Bouillabaisse (French)
    * Avgolemono Soup (Greek)
    * Harira (Moroccan)
* **Stews:**
    * Beef Tagine (Moroccan)
    * Chicken with Lemon and Olives (Greek)
    * Paella (Spanish)
    * Moussaka (Greek)
    * Ratatouille (French)
* **Hot Drinks:**
    * Turkish Coffee
    * Espresso (Italian)
    * Greek Mountain Tea
    * Salep (Turkish)
    * Horchata (Spanish)
